{"talk":{"id":57604,"name":"Nicola Jones: The dangers of a noisy ocean -- and how we can quiet it down","description":"The ocean is a naturally noisy place full of singing whales, grunting fish, snapping shrimp, cracking ice, wind and rain. But human-made sounds -- from ship engines to oil drilling -- have become an acute threat to marine life, says science journalist Nicola Jones. Watch (and listen) as she discusses the strange things that happen to underwater creatures in the face of ocean noise pollution -- and shares straightforward ways we can dial down the sound to see almost immediate impacts.","slug":"nicola_jones_the_dangers_of_a_noisy_ocean_and_how_we_can_quiet_it_down","recorded_at":"2019-07-20 00:00:00","published_at":"2020-03-11 15:03:00","updated_at":"2021-04-09 19:44:02","viewed_count":0,"emailed_count":0,"event":{"id":603,"name":"TEDSummit 2019"},"images":[{"image":{"size":"113x85","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/d8e7b60586e206905086261d6f8b831385fa3736_113x85.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"240x180","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/d8e7b60586e206905086261d6f8b831385fa3736_240x180.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"615x461","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/d8e7b60586e206905086261d6f8b831385fa3736_615x461.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"2400x1800","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/d8e7b60586e206905086261d6f8b831385fa3736_2400x1800.jpg"}}],"image_16x9":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/939b015d18b9d43aacd580de656d26cb69ffb73c_2880x1620.jpg","media":{"internal":{"64k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/NicolaJones_2019T-64k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":6454853,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"180k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/NicolaJones_2019T-180k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":17878821,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"320k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/NicolaJones_2019T-320k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc9